### Variables
@base_url = http://localhost:8000

### List All Providers
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/providers
Accept: application/json

### List Providers Filtered by Task (embedding)
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/providers?task=embedding
Accept: application/json

### List Providers Filtered by Task (llm)
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/providers?task=llm
Accept: application/json

### Connect to Provider (LM Studio)
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/providers/lmstudio/connect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_base": "http://localhost:1234/v1"
}

### Connect to Provider (Groq)
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/providers/groq/connect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_key": "gsk_your_api_key_here"
}

### Connect to Provider (OpenAI)
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/providers/openai/connect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_key": "sk-your-api-key-here"
}

### Connect to Provider (Ollama)
POST {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/providers/ollama/connect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "api_base": "http://localhost:11434/v1"
}

### List Models from Provider
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/providers/lmstudio/models
Accept: application/json


### List Models from Groq Provider
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/providers/groq/models
Accept: application/json

### Get Current Model Configuration
GET {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/config
Accept: application/json

### Set Embedding Model
PUT {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "task": "embedding",
  "provider_id": "lmstudio",
  "model_id": "text-embedding-nomic-embed-text-v1.5"
}

### Set LLM Model
PUT {{base_url}}/api/v1/models/config
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "task": "llm",
  "provider_id": "groq",
  "model_id": "qwen/qwen3-32b"
}
